Unconstrained

    No wires. No problems.                                                                 

Reactive

Fluidity in cursor movement corresponding to unit tilt sequences.

Full Connectivity

HC-05 bluetooth module will be able to establish communication with preferred laptop/machine.

User Display

OLED displays: relative 3d unit position, X-Y coordinates of cursor on screen.

Sustainable

Buck converter used to step down voltage of unit. Reduces unit's heat & extends the battery/lifetime.
